        },
        {
          "id": "phrase_002_ah_it_s_actually_m",
          "speaker": "Michael",
          "text": "Ah... it's actually my dad's place. He's been having some health problems, so I've sort of been stepping up.\nIt's been taking more out of me than I realized. I needed tonight.",
          "effects": [],
