        },
        {
          "id": "phrase_003_sounds_like_it_s_b",
          "speaker": "Diana",
          "text": "Sounds like it's been a lot.",
          "effects": [],
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "id": "phrase_004_it_s_mostly_fine_i",
          "speaker": "Michael",
          "text": "It's mostly fine, it just adds up.\nIt's easy to feel overlooked or taken for granted, y'know?",
