        },
        {
          "id": "phrase_002_what_if_i_m_inviti",
          "speaker": "Diana",
          "text": "What if I'm inviting you up because you make me feel the opposite?",
          "effects": [],
          "choices": []
        },
        {
          "id": "phrase_003_for_once_he_doesn_",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "For once, he doesn't answer quickly.\nHe looks at you the way he did earlier- careful and intent, like he understands the shape of what he's being handed and doesn't want to crush it by grabbing too fast.",
