        {
          "id": "phrase_005_the_stairs_up_to_y",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "The stairs up to your apartment are familiar, but you almost trip on them as you go up them.\nThoughts of what's about to happen flood your mind.\nThe door to your apartment clicks open.\nYou get the feeling that he's the kind of person who likes to take the room in when he walks into it- but he's far too focused on the shape of your body.\nThe feel of your body. Your breasts cupped in his hands, your hips unburdened by clothes and pressed against him.",
